<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Burkhard Hofner</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Anwesenheit am Sonntag nach Sonnwend zu Allersberg wegen des Schiedsgerichts mit den Örtel.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_226" id="111v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_226_r1l48">Burkhart Hofer </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_226_r1l49"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkhart / . Es ſol ein tag ſein / <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l50">den <hi rend="underlined">Örteln </hi> / auf den Suntag nach Sübenden cʒü <hi rend="underlined"><expan>Alerſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan></hi> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l51">auf <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag gen <expan>Alerſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd do beÿ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein wöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l52">vnd habt die müwe <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_226" id="111v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burkhart Hofer</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkhart, es sol ein tag sein
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den <hi rend="underlined">Örteln
                        </hi> auf den <app><note><q type="date">suntag nach sübenden</q>30.06.1409</note></app> czü <hi rend="underlined"><expan>Alersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan></hi>.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir auf
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag gen
                            <expan>Alersp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und do bey den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        sein wöllet und habt die müwe <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
